properties.Name: ExperianMajorLifeEvent
properties.Description:
A major change or event in life than can affect the credit or an individual.

Experian defines Major Life Events that are tracked.

Ex:
- Marriage
- Divorce
- Opening Small Business
- New College Student
- New To America

Columns.Name: ExperianMajorLifeEventId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Experian Major Life Event.

Columns.Name: ExperianMajorLifeName
Columns.Description: The name of a Experian Major Life Event.

Columns.Name: ExperianMajorLifeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Experian Major Life Event.
